item.title: GetOurData | Read Any API Like A Database
item.description: Ever been frustrated that it is so difficult to report on data that lives in SaaS software products or behind an API. BI tools are useless at connecting to APIs. GetOurData solves all this. It handles the many API authentication and pagination methods to connect and extract all your data from any API end point. It automatically parses the JSON API response and turns it into rows, columns, tables and table relationships and delivers it to you in an analytics-ready database format. Connect your BI tool of choice and visualize to your heart's content!
